l companies can enjoy this.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 28px;\"><b>\u201cThe species that survive are not the strongest, nor the fastest, nor the most intelligent; but those who accept better to the change \u201d.<\/b><\/p>\n<h2>Digital Transformation Road-map<\/h2>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vision, strategy, and leadership<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Senior management must sponsor the digitization process. This way, the company can show why the change is necessary and how it benefits the organization. It also offers appropriate means and resources to perform the process.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Business processes<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The change from an analog to the digital world has much deeper implications than the introduction of digital media in the company&#8217;s relationship with the customer; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/search-engine-optimization-seo-the-heart-of-your-online-success\">To achieve a true transformation towards a digital organization<\/a>, the internal processes of the company must be aligned with the process of change and digitized.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Technology<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The fundamental driver of this process of change is technology, it is essential to know in depth the possibilities that technology opens today in different fields such as Big Data, mobility, the internet of things, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/7-e-commerce-strategies-to-boost-up-your-business\"><strong>eCommerce<\/strong><\/a>, digital marketing, collaborative economies, business models.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_2292\" style=\"width: 544px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2292\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-2292\" src=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920.jpg\" alt=\"Digitization Transformation \" width=\"534\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-768x510.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-1536x1021.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-272x182.jpg 272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-2292\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Digitization Transformation<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Organization, team, and digital culture<\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is necessary to have a team of people with the necessary training; and skills to lead the digital transformation in the company. The most advanced organizations already have a specific managerial position to lead the change; the Chief Digital Officer, a profile halfway between strategy, business development, innovation, marketing, technology. But it is not enough to appoint a digital manager. It is necessary to remove the walls between different areas of the organization; and generate a culture of digital transformation through multi-disciplinary teams that build a joint vision.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Aryavrat<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is here to help in this Digital Transformation world, in order to approach the complex process of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/\">digitization of startups USA<\/a> with the maximum possible guarantees and achieve the objectives pursued, it is essential that the digital transformation is led with a global vision of the process from the understanding by senior management of the implications it has. indifferent aspects of the organization.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n    \"@id\": \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/what-is-digital-transformation-and-why-it-is-required\"\n  },\n  \"headline\": \"What is Digital Transformation and Why it is required ?\",\n  \"description\": \"Digital transformation is the strategic opportunity to incorporate new technologies in organizations that allow them to be more efficient\",\n  \"image\": [\n    \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digital_transformati_kPVFG.jpg\",\n    \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/digitization-4689528_1920-768x510.jpg\"\n  ],  \n  \"author\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Aryavrat Infotech Inc.\"\n  },  \n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Aryavrat Infotech Inc.\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/images\/arya-logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"2020-04-06\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2021-07-07\"\n}\n<\/script><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Digital transformation is the strategic opportunity to incorporate new technologies in organizations that allow them to be more efficient<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1999,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[201,5,7],"tags":[95,72,233,86,235,94,280,50,279],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v15.9 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>What 